<item>
            <title>[LU-12305] Lustre client mount filesystem ASSERTION  with SSK</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12305</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;1.when set ssk lctl conf_param testfs.srpc.flavor.o2ib.cli2mdt=ska or ski/skpi&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;lustre client&#160; mount&#160;&#160;filesystem ASSERTION&#160;&#160;&lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/attachment/32576/32576_lustre_client_crash_ska.txt&quot; title=&quot;lustre_client_crash_ska.txt attached to LU-12305&quot;&gt;lustre_client_crash_ska.txt&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;LustreError: 13302:0:(gss_sk_mech.c:342:sk_make_hmac()) ASSERTION( token-&amp;gt;len &amp;gt;= crypto_hash_digestsize(tfm) ) failed:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2.when set ssk lctl conf_param testfs.srpc.flavor.o2ib.cli2mdt=skn&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;lustre client&#160; mount&#160;&#160;filesystem ok,&#160; but umount&#160;ASSERTION&#160;&#160;&lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/attachment/32575/32575_lustre_client_crash_skn.txt&quot; title=&quot;lustre_client_crash_skn.txt attached to LU-12305&quot;&gt;lustre_client_crash_skn.txt&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3.&#160;when set ssk lctl conf_param testfs.srpc.flavor.o2ib.cli2mdt=gssnull&#160;&lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/attachment/32574/32574_lustre_client_crash_gssnull.txt&quot; title=&quot;lustre_client_crash_gssnull.txt attached to LU-12305&quot;&gt;lustre_client_crash_gssnull.txt&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;lustre client&#160; mount&#160; and umount filesystem ok,&#160; but&#160; try to mount&#160;filesystem again&#160; without finished.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
